# Blog Posts Directory

This directory contains blog posts that are automatically included in the sitemap.xml

## How to Add Blog Posts:

1. Create a new HTML or Markdown file in this directory
2. Name it with a URL-friendly slug (e.g., "crypto-scam-prevention-tips.html")
3. The sitemap will automatically detect and include it

## File Format:
- Supported: .html, .md
- Example: "preventing-crypto-scams.html"
- URL becomes: https://ciphertracers.com/blog/preventing-crypto-scams

## SEO Settings:
- Priority: 0.7 (blog posts)
- Change Frequency: monthly
- Last Modified: Automatically detected from file timestamp